{"tid":1506752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警：踢低跪下市民「自然反應」　開槍警「英勇克制」　為平定暴亂必須開槍","createTime":"2019-08-26T01:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:24:38.000Z","uid":37757,"like":19,"dislike":209,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"28d0e98fe1e15c73fdfb8aa5a953311d959251ee","tid":1506752,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/popo-13_8BJJg_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpopo-13_8BJJg_1200x0.png&h=10153fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃葵青大遊行演變成激烈警民衝突，荃灣更有警員向天開槍。警察公共關係科高級警司余鎧均今日凌晨見記者會，批評「暴徒」喪失理智、「近乎瘋狂」。余鎧均指出，拔槍警員踢低跪下市民是「自然反應」 ，形容開槍警「英勇克制」 ，為平定暴亂必須開槍。<br />\n<br />\n余鎧均解釋，「如果槍不是向天開，向暴徒開，可能無辜市民、記者，有可能受傷。」她形容，向天開槍是當時最好的做法，因當時情況「電光火石，生死一線之差」，近百名「暴徒」瘋狂式衝向警員。她未回應，開槍前，是否有警員跌下配槍。<br />\n<br />\n對於在場警員拔槍指向記者，她指出，記者在示威者及警方之間，當時是「非常時期」，「並不是日常工作可便利採訪」，又指有記者後面「暴徒」擲磚，需要示警。余鎧均解釋，警員開槍前「有做口頭警告」。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚開槍事件當中，有一名年長男街坊張開雙臂擋在警員及示威者中間，其後跪下並叫「唔好呀！」，被拔槍警一腳踢低。余鎧均回應指，當時警員留意一個人「停下有動作」，形容警員踢低市民是「自然反應」，最終行動是保護警務人員「自身安全」。<br />\n<br />\n余鎧均指出，晚上 7 時許，有示威者破壞一家麻雀館，用粗言恐嚇員工及市民，「行徑令人髮指」。至約 8 時，警車到場處理事件，警車內有警員鬟受襲受傷，之後衝鋒隊警員被過百名「暴徒」持棍、硬件等襲擊多次警告無效，因生命有威脅，有6 名警員拔出配槍戒備，一名警員向天開槍，無人中槍。她形容，開槍警表現「英勇克制」。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，昨日行動中共 15 名警員受傷。警方絕不容忍傷害他人、破壞社會安寧的行為，指行為不被任何文明社會所接受，「無論有什麼訴求，都唔應該合理化暴力。」警方希望記者配合執法，「為自己人身安全負責。」余鎧均指出，稍後補充被捕人數，未有證實是否有一名 12 歲男童被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/警-踢低跪下市民-自然反應-開槍警-英勇克制-為平定暴亂必須開槍/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6-%E8%B8%A2%E4%BD%8E%E8%B7%AA%E4%B8%8B%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89-%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6-%E8%8B%B1%E5%8B%87%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6-%E7%82%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%9A%B4%E4%BA%82%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=dd6988cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6-%E8%B8%A2%E4%BD%8E%E8%B7%AA%E4%B8%8B%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89-%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6-%E8%8B%B1%E5%8B%87%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6-%E7%82%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%9A%B4%E4%BA%82%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%2F&h=d90ba483\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/警-踢低跪下市民-自然反應-開槍警-英勇克制-為平定暴亂必須開槍/</a>"},{"pid":"24e33153bf0b39a6ee4dab6476592a906273d6b4","tid":1506752,"uid":255637,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />WFC 你都講左成2個月啦"},{"pid":"73cb985493984259d842db1fc735f4559b24147d","tid":1506752,"uid":188482,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"自然反應？我屌你老味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806757e7747dee1709fdd52f280d98daa09f25f1","tid":1506752,"uid":1374,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"73cb985493984259d842db1fc735f4559b24147d","tid":1506752,"uid":188482,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"自然反應？我屌你老味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:59:21.000Z","msg":"好正常啵 無人性既咪覺得自然反應囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ec8b436bfff46086b1b47f5a2b6d0c3e26bd2e","tid":1506752,"uid":36075,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"對暴政, 市民做所有野都係「自然反應」來的, 我DLLM AR 死黑狗...."},{"pid":"dd3276880cd85de37083dda2807c3f3b949fddba","tid":1506752,"uid":282569,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"自然反應都up 得出<br />\n黑警必須死全家"},{"pid":"1f19add85dbac20501d60d72396f7223d1296812","tid":1506752,"uid":62,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"佢地係咪真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚冷血"},{"pid":"0e42ffc3ea51f54e4bd6f9a89ba8453898a2ad47","tid":1506752,"uid":29899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=d741ff40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04fe2d11513da1b1b06aad2aa3d958bdc029dc94","tid":1506752,"uid":152987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"佢冇錯，呢啲係黑警嘅自然反應"},{"pid":"a9947bd07193118aee1016ed3a9517bffa4abea0","tid":1506752,"uid":1