ore":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"721又走撚到去唔開槍?????"},{"pid":"63d4157f911bae041d275d53dbb9286b539f3b12","tid":1506752,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"係又開槍唔係又開槍<br />\n咁呢邊應該可以開始囉刀斬過"},{"pid":"06c3cb033408ae912f30ec9d122b0454fc120702","tid":1506752,"uid":78087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"而家就係班狗做乜都有上頭死攬，龍門任佢擺<br />\n破窗效應，班狗會愈做愈狼死"},{"pid":"8849fd8192d6a60dde6b8b57b60f7dc9e05c5977","tid":1506752,"uid":166616,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d5e508f052473969ca7b3d4f2fbcae742e52ab","tid":1506752,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭閪 落地獄啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"b54b84cfd6531e132a86bc9eb045d49bc9858df9","tid":1506752,"uid":40624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"子彈如果是向天空發射，當到達最高點後，其下降是自由落體運動，其加速度是9.6米/S.S因此當其在其極限高度下落到地面時，其動能足可以擊穿人的頭骨而有餘，這個從一般工地作業中物體下落時傷人的道理是一樣的，如果在20米高度上掉落的一個M16以上的螺母，如果不戴安全帽，則足可以讓被擊中者頭破血流。嚴重的可能會擊穿頭骨的。子彈下落時的高度要幾百米甚至是上千米，那麼其下落時的動能是很大的。比這個要厲害的多了。"},{"pid":"7f82f4e98024d285cf7129cfdec177d2f7565638","tid":1506752,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ab72a25fc0b4612c7fc522901a9310573b9af1","tid":1506752,"uid":294648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"Madam&quot;我屌你老母&quot;都係自然反應"},{"pid":"6676185c26fcb0c8e5b0fcb831c4eafb04ff2d8f","tid":1506752,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:18:42.000Z","msg":"出火魔法係咪都係自然反應？"},{"pid":"86d0433ffce1ea3ad0095c0aca8f0923d01f6728","tid":1506752,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"原來腳踢赤手空拳、跪喺地下嘅人係「英勇克制」同「自然反應」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21da00e43a9e7dd8e1b5f9106446a29f9c7f865a","tid":1506752,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"一聽完佢咁講就想埋去車個madam兩巴，自然反應je"},{"pid":"9e2a778172178990aaa1ecd73eccddc930c257bb","tid":1506752,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"有第一槍就有第十槍"},{"pid":"c25d890ea820c19433fcf82be857f9d31ed382a9","tid":1506752,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"「係地下做左個動作」<br />\n係跪低呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"34f61d852b469a884ed58a05429592b30fe4d675","tid":1506752,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:27:58.000Z","msg":"而家借口都廢撚事諗<br />\n直接話鍾意打就打啦"},{"pid":"559714f4ab393f20f6ef31102326630adb8d3f72","tid":1506752,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[濕L晒，你要驚]防毒濾棉濕哂水會打柴，請立即更換</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506772\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506772</a><br />\n整合左啲濕水對濾棉影響嘅資料，大家幫手推比更多手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">利申:唔係呢方面專家，只係問人+整合資料，需要人實測</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n琴日落左成日大雨，好多裝修師傅都被迫做左海底奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然濾棉有一定「抗水」能力去過濾有毒蒸汽，但係「唉屌濕撚晒」之下都會打柴<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為防TL;DR 先寫結論:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n1. 外露濾棉如 2297/2097 + 單罐豬嘴3311K 等，如濕哂請即更換<br />\n2. 如501蓋 + 5N11 有外殼包下嘅，請打開檢查有無全濕<br />\n3. 內置濾棉嘅綜合濾罐 如60926/3系列，正路入水位唔多，但好睇實際有幾濕<br />\n4. 單純濾罐部份 如6006/3 系列，活性碳唔吸水，乾返應該唔大影響，有待實測<br />\n5. 雨天環境，重課可考慮502蓋 + 3M 7093 有殼防水式P100濾棉"},{"pid":"a7b149a53cb7e6d6a2151c47810b925aa7078959","tid":1506752,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12389475e361d30ebe5d8280f6def2216e2755e8","tid":1506752,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"一枝槍6粒彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68589cdb7aa838edadc33d7e5aed0a90f7571630","tid":1506752,"uid":154568,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"尋晚既抆槍事件中<br />\n其實大家可能忽略左一個重點<br />\n當抆槍指向人群時<br />\n佢地口中竟然唔係講&quot;咪走/退後&quot;去保護自己<br />\n而係一路向前行一路講<br />\n&quot;過黎啊！/打我啊！&quot;叫對方攻擊自己<br />\n<br />\n到底咁叫保護自己定係挑撥情緒呢?<br />\n真係英勇?<br />\n<br />\n自己上網搵反直播記錄睇下"},{"pid":"ad0f41121b985c0ffd415c78b12a6b76357f32d9","tid":1506752,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"Madam應該成日係狗屋跪低比大sir除褲拔槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c191aca905011c5b75bcd04972fa9cf5ed132172","tid":1506752,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:35:49.000Z","msg":"有示威者破壞一家麻雀館，用粗言恐嚇員工及市民，「行徑令人髮指」。<br />\n<br />\n黑警亂開鎗 亂打人 一樣用粗言恐嚇市民就唔令人髮指"},{"pid":"3814b6f4efa3a161b366276a876a78cff9c94f8f","tid":1506752,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"黑狗殺人都吹到英勇克制架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a5ab848aebcdee7957f3187aa4ad7ecb9257b4","tid":1506752,"uid":7270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"必須將新疆燈柱未成形前，連根拔起。行動方案討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"502002f2acfde3bbc2b7237c87474cdb12728